caption: I started going here because my previous spot was relaxed about pandemic safety measures. Now I won't stop getting food from Alladin's Kitchen. The food is really good and the staff are serious about safety.  We like the falafel (best falafel we've had on U Street), the jumbo slice, and the mozzarella sticks.
Do something Good For Yourself...Eat Here! I love this place! I was visiting and the food as well as the employees make me want to visit again. God Bless U!
Excellent food and Service Best food around... Try it u won't be disappointed
Got the specialty pizza and the beef kubeida and kabob, with added lamb. Everything was so good! Was very impressed with the pizza, which I wasn’t expecting. Will order from here again!

This was my go to place for a quick bite in DC—I live right around the corner.  However, I think they are under new ownership or something has went downhill in the last couple months.  They have lost my order twice and the staff never takes blame.  First they forgot to make an online order and I was told to place my orders by phone because they don’t watch their delivery apps.  The second time I ordered by phone.  If you want your food in a timely manner, I recommend going elsewhere.
Oj

GREAT GYROS!!!!! Make sure you ask for the green hot sauce on it or on the side. I'm surprised to see some less than stellar reviews for this place because the is basically my go to for Gyros (unless I feel like trekking the extra blocks to Zorbas.) The prices are good and the employees are always so kind. It's quick and easy. I've read that there may be some issues with quality control so if you go once and aren't satisfied, give them another try. They're in a very high traffic area of the city so I can see how if they're really busy, something could come out sub par, but I've always had a great experience here. Their pizza is really good too, I prefer it over Ducinis (next door) and jumbo slice (up the street). We also love the Kabobs but the Gyros are KING to me. FIVE STARS FOR SUREEEEE.
NOT BLACK OWNED... not sure why DoorDash and this restaurant refuse to change that falsehood

Absolutely Amazing!!!! Great food, attentive service, prime location!! Can't beat it!! The food is not only delicious but incredibly fresh (everything made to order) and a really healthy choice.  I first came here over the weekend and it was so good that I came back 3 times the following week, I even getting extra food to go for later! Even open LATE NIGHT with JUMBO SLICES!!!!  The first time I came, I got the Gyro Salad and it was so good! First of all, they have a ton of salad items and they let me get as much as I wanted. Second, they cut lamb off the spit and grilled it so it was really warm and juicy. Then I topped it off with their green sauce (no idea what it's made of) but it was delicious. The following times, I got the Greek pizza (trust me, GET IT!!!), baked chicken wings, and the kabobs. I haven't tried anything that I've been anything but extremely happy with. They do it right: keep the menu small but make everything really good! Try it, you won't regret it!!
